    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >拥有高度自定义的AI模拟</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款游戏中，你将观察定制的AI国家在一场混战中争夺全球霸权——游戏包含联盟、叛乱、傀儡政权以及各种政治曲折！<br><strong>注意：这不是策略游戏。</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/extras/2d09cc45c381e983087e7e26ed2f3e88.poster.avif?t=1763060732\" width=600 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/extras/2d09cc45c381e983087e7e26ed2f3e88.webm?t=1763060732\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/extras/2d09cc45c381e983087e7e26ed2f3e88.mp4?t=1763060732\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >强大的地图编辑器 + 上帝模式工具</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内置了预制地图和场景，但你也可以释放创造力，打造属于你自己的版本！地图和边界的复杂度完全由你决定！快来 Steam 创意工坊浏览数百个高质量场景，涵盖历史时期与奇幻世界！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/extras/f082cf73809ebef2a465690de1903e77.poster.avif?t=1763060732\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/extras/f082cf73809ebef2a465690de1903e77.webm?t=1763060732\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/extras/f082cf73809ebef2a465690de1903e77.mp4?t=1763060732\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过直接控制国家来主导世界历史。你可以在模拟过程中随时精细调整边界、国家属性、地形和AI行为！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >世界建筑</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >查看你模拟的完整历史与统计数据，更好地了解过去的事件和早已消失的国家。只要设置得当，世界可以持续演变数千年。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/extras/cb76cb447c387992cc046976ae0d35cb.poster.avif?t=1763060732\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/extras/cb76cb447c387992cc046976ae0d35cb.webm?t=1763060732\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/extras/cb76cb447c387992cc046976ae0d35cb.mp4?t=1763060732\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你对历史、地理、地图绘制，或者看着混乱蔓延感兴趣，《Ages of Conflict》一定能满足你！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
